blade. I said, I'm going to drive it. So he made a

15:59.367 --> 16:04.273
contraction where he, you know, it was a driver 
car. And he was a very good driver. He was a very good

16:06.977 --> 16:07.978
driver. And at first, Something was going wrong 
with the car, so he hired a mechanic to fix it.

16:19.300 --> 16:22.865
Pretty soon, he said, well, I'm not going to pay 
anybody just to do that. So he started working on

16:23.105 --> 16:25.348
that car. He used to break it all down, tear it apart 
completely, and then assemble it again. And you

16:31.335 --> 16:33.397
know, I mean, I can't do it. I can tear things apart, 
but I can't put them together again. And he used

16:39.204 --> 16:40.806
to... do a mechanic job very well, carpentry work, 
build anything, you know, things like that, he was

16:41.343 --> 16:53.561
pretty capable. Did he ever talk about any of the 
battles or any of the things that he did while he was

16:53.581 --> 16:58.308
fighting for Villa? No, like I said before, he 
never did talk to me too much about when he was a

16:58.548 --> 17:06.760
soldier, about his life when he was a soldier.

17:10.334 --> 17:12.917
