I don't remember. You know what he liked to do when 
he was in the crowd, conversations, something

17:24.990 --> 17:33.539
like that? He used to learn a lot of poems. He used to 
recite, like to recite poems and sing. He used to

17:41.143 --> 17:43.286
play guitar and used to sing. Do you remember what 
songs he sang? Oh, a lot of those Pajarito

17:49.273 --> 17:57.323
Barranqueño, La Edita.

